| `rs485.html` | RS485 configuration — baud rate, parity, register table |
| `sdcard.html` | SD Card manager — status, logging settings, file browser |
| `telegram.html` | Telegram bot — credentials, alerts, command reference |
| `login.html` | Authentication page |
| `style.css` | Shared stylesheet for all pages |
